{"readme":"<h1 class=\"title\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/stackgl/glslify-bundle\">glslify-bundle</a><div class=\"contrib\"></div></h1>\n<p><a href=\"http://github.com/badges/stability-badges\"></a></p>\n<p>Bundle a <a href=\"http://github.com/stackgl/glslify-deps\">glslify-deps</a> dependency tree into\na GLSL source string.</p>\n<p>This has been separated from <em>glslify-deps</em> such that you can prebundle a dependency\ntree server-side, but then still modify shader file contents in a browser.</p>\n<h2 id=\"usage\">Usage</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://nodei.co/npm/glslify-bundle/\"></a></p>\n<h3 id=\"source-bundle-deps-\"><code>source = bundle(deps)</code></h3>\n<p>Takes the output object from <a href=\"http://github.com/stackgl/glslify-deps\">glslify-deps</a>\nand returns a bundled GLSL string.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-javascript\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>var&#xA0;bundle&#xA0;=&#xA0;require(&apos;glslify-bundle&apos;)</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>var&#xA0;deps&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;=&#xA0;require(&apos;glslify-deps&apos;)</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>var&#xA0;path&#xA0;&#xA0;&#xA0;=&#xA0;require(&apos;path&apos;)</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>var&#xA0;file&#xA0;=&#xA0;path.join(__dirname,&#xA0;&apos;index.glsl&apos;)</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>deps().add(file,&#xA0;function(err,&#xA0;tree)&#xA0;{</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;if&#xA0;(err)&#xA0;throw&#xA0;err</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;var&#xA0;glsl&#xA0;=&#xA0;bundle(tree)</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;console.log(glsl)</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source js\"><span>})</span></span></div>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"contributing\">Contributing</h2>\n<p>See <a href=\"https://github.com/stackgl/contributing\">stackgl/contributing</a> for details.</p>\n<h2 id=\"license\">License</h2>\n<p>MIT. See <a href=\"http://github.com/stackgl/glslify-bundle/blob/master/LICENSE.md\">LICENSE.md</a> for details.</p>\n"}